                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010520-11-off56 t18010520-11-cd57"></join>, thirty-six quires of demy paper, value 30s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18010520-11-victim107" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Leonard
                  <interp inst="t18010520-11-victim107" type="surname" value="Leonard"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18010520-11-victim107" type="given" value="John"></interp>
